                 rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://w3id.org/arco/ontology/arco-lite> .


###  https://w3id.org/arco/ontology/arco-lite/isCollectionMemberOf
a-lite:isCollectionMemberOf rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
                            rdfs:subPropertyOf rico:isOrWasIncludedIn ;
                            rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://w3id.org/arco/ontology/arco-lite> .


###  https://w3id.org/arco/ontology/context-description/hasDating
a-cd:hasDating rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
